These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, van, bus, bike
1. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
2. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the bus##5
3. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | bike | tram | van | bus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, video-games, dancing, photography
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
2. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##5
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | photography | video-games | dancing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, paramedic, teacher, lawyer
1. the paramedic is on the right of the teacher##1
2. the paramedic is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pilot is the pilot##1
4. the pilot is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | lawyer | pilot | teacher | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
