2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | traveling | fishing | woodworking | photography |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, family, martial-arts, horror
1. the person watching family movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##2
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person watching horror movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | family | horror | adventure |

