3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | woodworking | reading | rock-climbing | video-games |

