.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, guinea-pig, goldfish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the mouse##2
3. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | hedgehog | guinea-pig | mouse | goldfish |

